<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body>
    <h2>The html script tag</h2>
    <p>We use the script tag to create a JavaScript code inside the html document.</p>
    <p>Common uses for JavaScript are image manipulation, form validation, and dynamic changes of content.</p>
    <button onclick="myFunc()">Click the button</button>
    <p id="motor"></p>
    <script>
      function myFunc(){
        document.getElementById("motor").innerHTML="This is my JavaScript script."
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>

